Date: Fri, 21 Jun 2024 17:40:41 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] x86/its: Enumerate Indirect Target Selection (ITS) bug
References: bsc#1234429
Patch-mainline: 6.12.29
Git-commit: 159013a7ca18c271ff64192deb62a689b622d860

commit 159013a7ca18c271ff64192deb62a689b622d860 upstream.

ITS bug in some pre-Alderlake Intel CPUs may allow indirect branches in the
first half of a cache line get predicted to a target of a branch located in
the second half of the cache line.

Set X86_BUG_ITS on affected CPUs. Mitigation to follow in later commits.

